::Halucigen::
Halucigen smiles as the bot accedently looks in his eyes. He fires two
feather missiles from his wind locking on to the two missiles blowing
them up before they got to Halucigen.
"Prowl is it."
Halucigen was able to gather a few things about his enemy in the
glance and enough to learn of his worst ngihtmare.
He focused again on the bot trying to make his nightmare become a
reality...in Prowls mind.
